Lists stored assets (files) by type.

Source: R/list_assets_by_type.R
list_assets_by_type.Rd

Lists stored assets (files) by type.

list_assets_by_type(vol_id = 1, type = "video", vb = FALSE)

Arguments

vol_id

Volume ID

type

Data file type, e.g. "video", "pdf", or "csv"

vb

A boolean value. If TRUE provides verbose output.

Value

Data frame with the selected asset types.

Examples

list_assets_by_type()
